  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create-extra-casing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/yEGVcr59?color=34D058&amp;label=Modrinth%20Downloads&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create-extra-casing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1192187?color=FC7303&amp;label=CurseForge%20Downloads&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/Reggarfgod/create_extra_casing/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/issues/Reggarfgod/create_extra_casing?color=6E40C9&amp;label=Issues&amp;logo=github\"></a> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/430776550443581450?color=5865F2&amp;label=Online%20Users&amp;logo=discord\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://zap-hosting.com/reggarf\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1010929/description_2dbdedf7-e1a0-4bcd-86a6-01c26447af70.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"678\" height=\"87\"></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><br>THANKS TO OUR SPONSORS</strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>THANKS TO ZAP-HOSTING! Use code Reggarf-1047 for 20% off any order!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">https://zap-hosting.com/reggarf</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">CREATE</span>:</strong><strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">EXTRA </span><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">CASING</span></strong></h1>\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3><strong>List of All Casings in Create: Extra Casing</strong></h3>\n<p>This mod introduces a variety of <strong>colorful casings</strong> to enhance the visual appeal of your Create builds. Each casing retains the <strong>functionality of standard casings</strong> but comes in unique color variations to match different themes and styles.</p>\n<h4><strong>Available Casings:</strong></h4>\n<p>🎨 <strong>Primary Colors:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>🔴 <strong>Red Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🔵 <strong>Blue Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🟡 <strong>Yellow Casing</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎨 <strong>Secondary Colors:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>🟠 <strong>Orange Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🟢 <strong>Green Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🟣 <strong>Purple Casing</strong></li>\n<li><strong>🌸 Magenta Casing</strong></li>\n<li><strong>🧊 Cyan Casing</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎨 <strong>Neutral &amp; Grayscale Tones:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>⚫ <strong>Black Casing</strong></li>\n<li>⚪ <strong>White Casing</strong></li>\n<li><strong>🟤 Brown Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🌑 <strong>Gray Casing</strong></li>\n<li>🌫️ <strong>Light Gray Casing</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎨 <strong>Pastel Variations:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>💗 <strong>Pink Casing</strong></li>\n<li>💙 <strong>Light Blue Casing</strong></li>\n<li>💚&nbsp;<strong>lime Casing</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each of these casings can be used to <strong>build, customize, and organize your Create machinery</strong>, bringing new aesthetics and functionality to your contraptions.</p>\n<p>Would you like any <strong>specific color additions or texture effects</strong> to be included? 😊</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><a href=\"https://zap-hosting.com/createletscreate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1010929/description_6bc26b56-9563-428f-9ac8-41c9f43ff6a2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\"></a></strong></span></h1>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
